{"tid":2306845,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［蘋果獨家｜文革2.0］考評局歷史科經理離職，懷疑試題一早外洩","createTime":"2020-11-30T17:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T17:50:26.000Z","uid":211994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5881defe661c85b54864d60065b71c26a737f8cc","tid":2306845,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係爆咗咩大鑊出嚟，但我相信蘋果牌牙膏必有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n...希望唔會好似上次停課咁樣又估錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文憑試歷史科開考前一日，左派媒體翻出楊穎宇「沒有日本侵華，哪有新中國？忘本呀！」的Facebook帖文批鬥，翌日才揭盅的試題「1900-45年間，日本為中國帶來利多於弊」出爐後，<span class=\"gold\">當晚立即被教育局發聲明譴責</span>。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，楊穎宇向同事<span class=\"gold\">形容事情非常巧合</span>，質疑試題早於開考前已被洩漏，其後該題的評卷參考更被《文匯報》公開，連串洩漏事件令他感到在考評局工作已不再安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/76TJAJBXSZGAVKTMYQHGUFDCQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2F76TJAJBXSZGAVKTMYQHGUFDCQI%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xFRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=0676c032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2F76TJAJBXSZGAVKTMYQHGUFDCQI%2F&h=65cc9348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/76TJAJBXSZGAVKTMYQHGUFDCQI/</a>"},{"pid":"d9268f00d7b76f5897d08629bce9cb9a987b58b7","tid":2306845,"uid":211994,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文憑試所有答卷都會被掃描，讓閱卷員在到評核中心在網上改卷。由於最終考評局「跪低」決定取消試題，據悉，楊穎宇向同事透露，他本人須親手在系統中遮蔽考生就該題所寫答案，坦言這是他從事考評工作多年以來所做過最可恥的事，其間更看到有考生就該題寫下多達數頁的答案，令他在遮蔽這些答案的過程中，多次流下男兒淚。"},{"pid":"6e981b6d344f9b8905b989ec1011b272843239bd","tid":2306845,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e55233ff265e9dd5dd742cec33c9551d6d2a554c","tid":2306845,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e37d40c92c63a48a2776d4d19800187ccebd318","tid":2306845,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51af21c77da92849ae78b78fc1aa4fd45a33f98b","tid":2306845,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"考評局日前公佈，已聘任<del>內地</del><span class=\"xx-large\">支那</span>出身的嶺南大學經濟學系教授魏向東為下任秘書長，將於明年3月履新。"},{"pid":"5445d40bb0672b46c262372f96779c679ccae693","tid":2306845,"uid":312114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"幾年前見過真人，毫無官僚氣，好有見解同諗法。"},{"pid":"80dc9f3e6125e8c10564da763c888bb1fee13117","tid":2306845,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"「沒有日本侵華，哪有新中國？忘本呀！」<br />\n<br />\n明明係事實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無日本侵華你共產黨一早比老蔣打到渣都無"},{"pid":"2b503c8918764b246a563e81586e447251b734cc","tid":2306845,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80dc9f3e6125e8c10564da763c888bb1fee13117","tid":2306845,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"「沒有日本侵華，哪有新中國？忘本呀！」<br />\n<br />\n明明係事實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無日本侵華你共產黨一早比老蔣打到渣都無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"毛澤東自己講"}],"pinned":{"pid":"51af21c77da92849ae78b78fc1aa4fd45a33f98b","tid":2306845,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"考評局日前公佈，已聘任<del>內地</del><span class=\"xx-large\">支那</span>出身的嶺南大學經濟學系教授魏向東為下任秘書長，將於明年3月履新。"}}